                        modelFields="[text@richtext]"
                        name="Text Container Text"
                        text="&lt;p>We welcome your feedback on the accessibility of AbbVie.com and AbbVie’s other websites. Please let us know if you encounter any accessibility issues on an AbbVie website or have a suggestion for improving the accessibility or usability of a website by contacting us using one of the methods below. Please make sure to reference the particular website at issue and describe the specific feature you feel is not fully accessible or suggest an improvement:&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xa; &lt;li>&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.abbvie.com/contactus.html&quot;>Contact Form&lt;/a>&lt;/li>&#xa; &lt;li>E-mail:  &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:webaccessibility@abbvie.com&quot;>webaccessibility@abbvie.com&lt;/a>&lt;/li>&#xa; &lt;li>Postal Address: 1 North Waukegan Road, North Chicago, IL, 60064&lt;/li>&#xa;&lt;/ul>"/>
