                        text="&lt;p>Accessibility of our websites rely on the following technologies to work with the particular combination of web browser and any assistive technologies or plugins installed on your computer:&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xa; &lt;li>HTML&lt;/li>&#xa; &lt;li>WAI-ARIA&lt;/li>&#xa; &lt;li>CSS&lt;/li>&#xa; &lt;li>JavaScript&lt;/li>&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xa;&lt;p>These technologies are relied upon for conformance with the accessibility standards used.&lt;/p>"/>
